      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MEPUNGA VELVET (2) had the drop on the lead from the rails draw last start but could only manage third, beaten 11 lengths (30.16) at Sandown in a Mix 6/7 over 515m. Some good form is emerging from her last run. Can measure up this time. PAW VINE (4) was out of the frame on debut then improved with an effortless maiden success as she ran right away to score at this track (23.51). Should be in this for a long way. DODGE THE DREAM (1) doesn't win out of turn but recent form sound. Has been in the minors the last two runs, the latest finishing third (23.93) at this track. Has performed well from this box with a win and two minor placings to her name from three starts. Bold showing expected. WESTAR LEO (3) should be thereabouts despite an unplaced run here most recently.",
